# RAGfly — Environment variables
# Copy to .env, fill in, and load with: source .env
# NEVER commit .env with real values. Add .env to .gitignore.

# --- Operational (used on every call) ---
RAGFLY_API_URL=https://api.ragfly.ai
RAGFLY_API_KEY=slm_live_...          # your API key — the only credential agents need

# --- Bootstrap only (used once, to mint the API key above) ---
# After you have RAGFLY_API_KEY you can delete these two lines.
RAGFLY_EMAIL=you@email.com
RAGFLY_PASSWORD=YourPassword

# --- Optional: open original files on disk (web-uploaded docs only) ---
# Parent folder of the folder you uploaded via the web app. RAGfly never reads
# nor stores it. Only needed if your agent opens the ORIGINAL file on disk.
# See ENV_VARS.md / MCP.md for the full explanation.
# RAGFLY_ROOT=/Users/you/Dropbox
